      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nInitial testing succeeded.\n\nSucceeded:\n- sanity1@ldiskfs+DNE sanity2@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-slow@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special1@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special1@ldiskfs sanity-special2@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special2@ldiskfs sanity-special3@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special3@ldiskfs sanity-special4@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special4@ldiskfs sanity-special5@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special5@ldiskfs sanity-special6@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special6@ldiskfs sanity-special7@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special7@ldiskfs sanity-special8@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special8@ldiskfs sanity-special9@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special9@ldiskfs sanity-special10@ldiskfs+DNE sanity-special10@ldiskfs sanity1@zfs sanity2@zfs sanity-slow@zfs sanity-special1@zfs sanity-special1@zfs+DNE sanity-special2@zfs sanity-special2@zfs+DNE sanity-special3@zfs sanity-special3@zfs+DNE sanity-special4@zfs sanity-special4@zfs+DNE sanity-special5@zfs sanity-special5@zfs+DNE sanity-special6@zfs sanity-special6@zfs+DNE sanity-special7@zfs sanity-special7@zfs+DNE sanity-special8@zfs sanity-special8@zfs+DNE sanity-special9@zfs sanity-special9@zfs+DNE sanity-special10@zfs sanity-special10@zfs+DNE \n\n(centos7)All results and logs: https://testing.whamcloud.com/gerrit-janitor/29790/results.html\nNo additional testing was requested",
